name: Bursts
description: Great for a big empty wall!  One of a kind, abstract, original, signed by Ann.   Acrylic paint on canvas.  Bright, multi-colored bursts pop against a white background.  Has a very raised textured feel to it.  Ann uses her hands and fingers instead of brushes to create all of her paintings.  "Feeling the paint provides a direct connection to my creative intuition.  I never know what I'll end up with.  I just trust my instincts, my hands and enjoy the process."  Medium canvas size is 21 7/8" x 27 7/8".  Comes unframed.  Shipping and handling is additional
